A document-based Q&A application that lets users ask questions directly from uploaded text or PDF documents.
It uses LangChain, OpenAI GPT-3.5, and Chroma vector storage to retrieve and generate accurate answers from document content.

Key Features:

Loads and splits documents into smaller chunks for effective retrieval.

Generates semantic embeddings using SentenceTransformerEmbeddings.

Stores and retrieves document embeddings using Chroma.

Utilizes RetrievalQA chain for context-aware responses.

Simple Streamlit UI for user input and dynamic query answering.
